  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 28080,
      "text": "传说远古的梵天神殿里，立着三根金刚石柱子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "一根柱子上，从下到上套着六十四个由大到小的金盘。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.45,
      "size": 55152,
      "text": "僧侣们要把整摞金盘搬到另一根柱子，规则很简单：一次只搬一个，大盘永远不能压在小盘上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "recursion",
      "line_id": "rec-1",
      "filename": "recursion-rec-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/xiaoxiao/recursion-rec-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "面对很多盘子，聪明的办法是先假装最大的盘不存在。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "recursion",
      "line_id": "rec-2",
      "filename": "recursion-rec-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/xiaoxiao/recursion-rec-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "想办法把上面的 n 减 1 个盘子，借助中间柱先挪到旁边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "recursion",
      "line_id": "rec-3",
      "filename": "recursion-rec-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/xiaoxiao/recursion-rec-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.74,
      "size": 43776,
      "text": "再把最大的盘直接放到目标柱，最后把那 n 减 1 个盘搬过来盖上，这就是递归。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "steps",
      "line_id": "step-1",
      "filename": "steps-step-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/xiaoxiao/steps-step-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.01,
      "size": 48096,
      "text": "设搬 n 个盘要 T 步，那么搬 n 加 1 个，就得先搬走 T 步、放大盘一步、再搬回 T 步。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "steps",
      "line_id": "step-2",
      "filename": "steps-step-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/xiaoxiao/steps-step-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.4,
      "size": 38448,
      "text": "于是步数每次翻一倍还多一步，算下来正好是 2 的 n 次方减 1。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "steps",
      "line_id": "step-3",
      "filename": "steps-step-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/xiaoxiao/steps-step-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.4,
      "size": 38448,
      "text": "三个盘要七步，四个盘十五步，五个盘三十一步，一步都省不掉。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "doom",
      "line_id": "doom-1",
      "filename": "doom-doom-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/xiaoxiao/doom-doom-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "传说僧侣搬完六十四个金盘之时，就是世界末日。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "doom",
      "line_id": "doom-2",
      "filename": "doom-doom-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/xiaoxiao/doom-doom-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.45,
      "size": 39168,
      "text": "可六十四个盘要 2 的 64 次方减 1 步，那是一千八百多亿亿次移动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "doom",
      "line_id": "doom-3",
      "filename": "doom-doom-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tower-of-hanoi/xiaoxiao/doom-doom-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.52,
      "size": 40320,
      "text": "哪怕每秒搬一个盘，也要五千八百多亿年，宇宙都还没这么老，尽可放心。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tower-of-hanoi",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
